        <paragraph>If your editor supports the <reference name="language server protocol" refuri="https://microsoft.github.io/language-server-protocol/">language server protocol</reference>,
            you can use <reference name="clangd" refuri="https://clangd.llvm.org">clangd</reference> for completion, diagnostics, and more.
